    <body>
    
<l><pb facs="142"/><lb n="5" />kaṭalkuṟai paṭuttanīr kalkuṟai paṭaveṟin</l>
<l>tuṭalē ṟurumiṉa mārppa malai<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark>mālai</l>
<l>muṟṟupu muṟṟupu veyti mutirmukil</l>
<l>poru<lb n="6" />tikal pulipōḻnta pūnuta leḻilyāṉaik</l>
<l>kurutikkōṭ ṭaḷikaṟai teḷipeṟak kaḻīiyiṉṟu -</l>
<l>kālaik kaṭalpaṭintu kāykatirōṉ pōyavaḻi</l>
<l>mālai malaimaṇantu maṇṭu<lb n="7" />yiṉṟa kaṅkulāṉ</l> 
<l>vāṉāṟṟu maḻaitalaii maraṉāṟṟu malarnāṟṟan</l>
<l>tēṉāṟṟu maṇanāṟṟañ ceṟuveyi luṟukālai</l>
<l>kāṉāṟṟuṅ kārnāṟṟaṅ komputirtta kaḷināṟṟan</l> 
<l>tāṉāṟṟaṅ kalantuṭaṉ<lb n="8" /> ṟaḻīivantu tarūumvaiyai -</l>
<l>taṉṉāṟṟa mītu taṭampoḻi ṟāṉyāṟṟu</l>
<l>vennāṟṟu vēcaṉai nāṟṟaṅ kutukutuppa</l>
<l>vūrūr paṟaiyoli koṇṭaṉ ṟuyarmatili</l>
<l>ṉī<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>rūr vāra</l>
<l>tiraṇṭērp<pb facs="143"/><lb n="1" /> puravi vaṅkam pūṭṭavum</l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>p pāṇṭiyiṟ ṟaṇṭē rūravum</l>
<l>vayamāp paṇṇunar matamāp paṇṇavuṅ</l> 
<l>kayamāp pēṇi kalavā tūravu</l>
<l>mukaḷir kōtai maintar puṉaiyavu</l> 
<l>maintar taṇṭār makaḷi<lb n="2" />r peyyavu</l> 
<l>muntuṟal viruppoṭu muṟaimaṟan taṇintava</l> 
<l>rāṭuvār poyta laṇivaṇ ṭimirmaṇaṟ</l>
<l>kōṭē ṟoruttat tirumpuṉa liṟkuṟuti</l>
<l>māṭa maṟukiṉ maruvi maṟukuṟak</l>
<l>kūṭal viḻaiyun<lb n="3" /> takaittut takaivaiyai -</l>
<l>pukaivakai taiiviṉār pūṅkōtai nallār</l>
<l>takaivakai taiiyiṉār</l>
<l>mālai mikamikac maṟṟaiya maṟṟaiya</l>
<l>cūṭṭuṅ kaṇṇiyu mōṭṭu valaiyamu</l>
<l>miyala<lb n="4" />ṇi yaṇiniṟpa vēṟiyama rarippi</l>
<l>ṉiyalaya laṇinōkki yāṅkāṅku varupava</l>
<l>rīivaḷai yāramō ṭittā ṉuṭaṉākak</l>
<l>keṭuvaḷai pūṇṭavaṇ mēṉiyiṟ kaṇṭu</l>
<l>nontavaṇ<lb n="5" /> māṟṟā ḷivaḷeṉa nōkkat</l>	
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>nta kaḷvaṉ camaḻppu mukaṅkāṇmiṉ -</l>
<l>vāḷi cerucceyta cīṟṟat tavaiyavaiyaṉṉa</l> 
<l>nērita ḻuṇkaṇār niṟaikā ṭāka</l>
<l>vōṭi yo<lb n="6" />ḷittoyyap pōvā ṇilaikāṇmiṉ -</l>
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>oyyappō vāḷai yuṟaḻntōḷiv vāṇutal</l>
<l>vaiyai maṭut<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark>tāṟ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṭaleṉat teyya</l>
<l>neṟimaṇa ṉēṭiṉar<lb n="7" /> cellacce lēṟṟac</l> 
<l>ceṟiniraippeṇ valluṟaḻ piyātu toṭarpeṉṉa</l> 
<l>maṟaliṉāṇ māṟṟāṇ makaḷ</l>
<l>vāyvāḷā niṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>ceṟinakai cittan tikaittu -</l>
<l>āyat torutti ya<lb n="8" />vaḷai yamarkāma</l>
<l>māyappoy kūṭṭi mayakki vilaikkaṇikai</l>
<l><g ref="#kompu"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṇmaip potumaip piṇaiyili yaimpulattait</l> 
<l>tuṟṟuva tuṟṟun tuṇaiyitaḻ vāyttoṭṭi</l>
<l>muṟṟā naṟunaṟā moy<pb facs="144"/><lb n="1" />puṉa lāṭṭik</l> 
<l>kārikai nīrēr va<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṟ kaḷirmak kaḷināñciṉ</l>
<l>mūri tavira muṭukku mutucāṭi</l>
<l>maṭamata raṇkaṇ kayiṟāka vaittut</l>
<l>taṭameṉṟōṭ ṭoṭṭut tataitumaṭa viralā</l> 
<l>li<lb n="2" />ṭṭārk kiyāḻārttum pāṇiyi lemmiḻaiyait</l> 
<l>toṭṭārttu miṉpat tuṟaippo tuvikeṭṭakaip</l>
<l>poytaṉ makaḷirkaṇ kāṇa vikuttantiv</l>
<l>vaiyait toḻuvattut<lb n="3" /> tantu vaṭittiṭittu</l>
<l><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ttikai mālaiyā<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark> mōki yavaiyattut</l>
<l>toṭarntem merutu toḻilceyyā tō</l>
<l>viṭuṅkaṭaṉ vēḷāḷark kiṉṟu paṭarntiyān</l>
<l>taṉ<lb n="4" />mārpat taṇṭan tarumārat tāṇmārpu</l>
<l>niṉmārpu mōrotta nīrmaiyako leṉṉāmuṉ</l>
<l>tēṭiṉā rēcac cilamakaḷir maṟṟataṟ</l>
<l>kūṭiṉār vaiyai yakattu -</l>
<l>cin<lb n="5" />tikkat tīrum piṇiyāṭ ceṟēṟka</l>
<l>maintuṟṟāy veñcoṉ maṭamayiṟ cāyalai</l>
<l>vantikka vāreṉa maṉaṟakka nōyitu</l>
<l>vēṟṟārai yēṟṟār toḻuta liḷivaravu<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark></l> 
<l><lb n="6" />pōṟṟāykā ṇaṉṉai puraiyōy puraiyiṉṟu</l>
<l>māṟṟāḷai māṟṟāḷ varavu -</l>
<l>a<space quantity="3" unit="character"/> co ṉallavai kāṇāmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟantu muḻaviṉ varuvāynīya vāyvāḷā</l>
<l>ventaiyeṉak kī<lb n="7" />tta viṭuvaḷai yārappūṇ</l>
<l>vantavaḻi niṉpāṉ māyak kaḷavaṉṟēṟ</l>
<l>ṟantāṉait tantē tarukku -</l>
<l>mālai yaṇiya vilaitantāṉ mātaßniṉ</l>
<l>kāla cilampuṅ kaḻaṟṟuvāṉ cōlai</l>
<l>yatiralaṅ kaṇṇi<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark><lb n="8" />nī yaṉpaṉeṟ kaṟpaṉ</l>
<l>katuvā yavaṉkaḷvaṉ kaḷviṉā ṉallēṉ -</l>
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>vacciya māṉē maṟaliṉai māṟṟumakku</l>
<l>nacciṉā ripavai nāṭaṟiya nummavē</l>
<l>cēkkai yiṉiyārpāṟ celvāṉ mā<pb facs="145"/><lb n="1" />ṉaiyāḷāṟ</l>
<l>kā kaṭintoḻukal kūṭumō kūṭā</l>
<l>takavuṭai maṅkaiyar cāṉṟāṇmai cāṉṟā</l> 
<l>rikaḻiṉuṅ kēḷvarai yētti yiṟaiñcuvāri</l>
<l>ṉikaḻva taṟiyātu nilluni ṉallāy</l>
<l>makaḷirai<lb n="2" /> maintuṟṟu mārpuṟṟa mainta</l>
<l>rakalaṅ kaṭikuvē meṉpavai yārkkāṉu</l>
<l>muṭiporu ḷaṉṟu muṉiyaṉ muṉiyal</l>
<l>kaṭavarai niṟkumō kāmaṅ koṭiyiyalāy -</l>
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>iṉṉa tu<lb n="3" />ṉiyum pulaviyu mēṟpikkun</l>
<l>teṉṉavaṉ vaiyaic ciṟappu -</l>
<l>koṭiyiyalār kaipōṟ kuvinta mukai -</l>
<l>aravuṭaṉ ṟa<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark>vaipōl virinta kulai -</l>
<l>kuṭaivirin tavai<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark><lb n="4" />pōlak kōlu malar</l> 
<l>cuṉaikaḻintu tūṅkuvaṉa nīriṉ malar -</l>
<l>ciṉaivirin tutirntavīyē putalviri yōtoṭu</l> 
<l>maruvi<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark> corinta tiraiyiṟ ṟurantu</l>
<l>neṭumāl curuṅ<lb n="5" />kai naṭuvaḻip pōntu</l> 
<l>kaṭumā kaḷiṇaittuk kaiviṭunīr pōlu</l>
<l>neṭunīr malipuṉa ṉīṇmāṭak kūṭaṟ</l>
<l>kaṭimatil peyyum poḻutu -</l>
<l>nāmama rūṭalu naṭpun taṇappuṅ</l>
<l><lb n="6" />kāmamuṅ kaḷḷuṅ kalantuṭaṉ pārāṭṭit</l>
<l>tāmamar kātalō ṭāṭap puṇarvittal</l>
<p>xml:id="Pari20-intro"pūmali vaiyaik kiyalpu</l> – என்பது – பருவவரவின்கட் தலைமகள தாற்றா<metamark function="line-filler">௦</metamark><lb n="7" />மை கண்டு தூதுவிடச் சென்ற பாணன் றலைமகற்குக் கார்ப்பருவம் வையை நர்விழவணியுங் கூறியது – ஆசிரிய நலந்துவனார் பாட்டு – நல்லச்சுதனா ரிசை – பண் காந்தாரம் <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/></p>    
